力狀態，呢個時候需要肌肉處於收縮狀態去拉長佢，即係變成橡筋，咁拉力就可以分佈去任何一處地方，講咁多呢樣野即係「離心收縮」<br />\n<br />\n好老土既講法就係話運動完第二日酸痛（遲發性肌肉酸痛-DOMS）係因為乳酸，麻煩update下呢個已經錯左幾十年，最近既研究係指呢個痛唔係肌肉痛而係肌肉外包膜既筋膜發炎，有興趣可以去睇下<br />\n<br />\nDOMS特點係主要由離心收縮訓練引起，首次訓練後最痛然後隨次數增加DOMS漸漸減少至無，呢個情況筋膜學解釋就係肌肉要處於收縮狀態去拉長先真正可以拉到啲筋膜，刺激到筋膜受損再回復生長，筋膜強化修補完再做相同動作就唔會再DOMS<br />\n<br />\n而實驗都表明阻力訓練對增加肌肉長度既效果唔比靜態拉筋差<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/oCSv5ow0l-w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FoCSv5ow0l-w&d=RGPktlJYpqjIeXpZRAkgw7%2BiaDmtBxIfZa%2Bp1tlHcc8%3D&h=89fe6ef6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/oCSv5ow0l-w</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://running.biji.co/index.php?q=news&amp;act=info&amp;id=94024&amp;subtitle=%E3%80%90%E6%9B%B8%E6%91%98%E3%80%91%E8%82%8C%E7%AD%8B%E8%86%9C%E8%A8%93%E7%B7%B4%E8%88%87%E3%80%8C%E8%82%8C%E8%82%89%E7%97%A0%E7%97%9B%E3%80%8D%E6%96%B0%E8%A7%A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frunning.biji.co%2Findex.php%3Fq%3Dnews%26act%3Dinfo%26id%3D94024%26subtitle%3D%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%259B%25B8%25E6%2591%2598%25E3%2580%2591%25E8%2582%258C%25E7%25AD%258B%25E8%2586%259C%25E8%25A8%2593%25E7%25B7%25B4%25E8%2588%2587%25E3%2580%258C%25E8%2582%258C%25E8%2582%2589%25E7%2597%25A0%25E7%2597%259B%25E3%2580%258D%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%25A7%25A&d=RGPktlJYpqjIeXpZRAkgw7%2BiaDmtBxIfZa%2Bp1tlHcc8%3D&h=ba1126a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://running.biji.co/index.php?q=news&amp;act=info&amp;id=94024&amp;subtitle=%E3%80%90%E6%9B%B8%E6%91%98%E3%80%91%E8%82%8C%E7%AD%8B%E8%86%9C%E8%A8%93%E7%B7%B4%E8%88%87%E3%80%8C%E8%82%8C%E8%82%89%E7%97%A0%E7%97%9B%E3%80%8D%E6%96%B0%E8%A7%A</a>"},{"pid":"419a98e70e967f42bf0f0dbddc18092707a89845","tid":2443609,"uid":198503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb0c37cdea91864922110e9def4bfd1d42c87b84","tid":2443609,"uid":275698,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c8a6830d4bcbc78b608102d0f1071f6b268179f1","tid":2443609,"uid":47614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19547d98971720121360def5851bca13d4f4bfcd",